The SACP confirmed today that President Jacob Zuma had informed them that he intends to fire Finance Minister Pravin Gordhan."The president informed us of his intention to effect a Cabinet reshuffle, replacing both minister and deputy minister of finance," SACP first deputy general secretary Solly Mapaila told reporters in Johannesburg.&nbsp; The SACP met ANC officials for talks on Monday.&nbsp;More to follow.http://www.news24.com/SouthAfrica/News/zuma-told-us-he-intends-to-fire-gordhan-sacp-20170330